'''關西蒙'''（{{lang-en|Simon Kwan Sai Mung，12月31日}}），前[[香港|香港]][[香港商業電台|商業電台]]唱片騎師，是組合「[[六啤半|六啤半]]」的成員。在1970年代末到1980年代初曾經在電台及電視台當紅，在[[電視廣播有限公司|無線電視]]的電視劇《[[愛情安歌|愛情安歌]]》裡擔綱演出。現時去向未明，傳聞他成為了玄學家。

==背景==
關西蒙早年就讀[[格致書院_(香港)|格致書院]]，在校時喜歡唱歌。1976年參加[[商業電台|商業電台]]主辦的第四屆全港公開業餘歌唱比賽奪得「歐西曲組」亞軍<ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59%2F9WIUSQ5l7%2FhBObdJt86Q&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=34&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc 商台歌唱比賽 總決賽有結果] {{Wayback|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59%2F9WIUSQ5l7%2FhBObdJt86Q&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=34&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%B3%95%E8%98%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%BC%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc |date=20210715134013 }} [[華僑日報|華僑日報]]. 1976-09-16</ref>及由[[市政局|市政局]]與[[香港電台|香港電台]]合辦的全港業餘歌唱比賽「民歌合唱組」亞軍<ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59%2F9WIUSQ5l742dB5YsYfbm&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=5&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc 業餘歌唱比賽 得獎名單公佈] {{Wayback|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59%2F9WIUSQ5l742dB5YsYfbm&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=5&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc |date=20211104163047 }} [[華僑日報|華僑日報]]. 1976-10-30</ref>，中學畢業後加入香港商業電台任職唱片騎師，1980年成為「[[六啤半|六啤半]]」的成員，並曾推出相關專輯。其主持風格以專說人生哲理為主<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rthk9.rthk.hk/broadcast75/topic05c.htm |title=廣播穿梭75年 - DJ風格 |date=2003 |website= |publisher=香港電台 |access-date=2021-06-22 |quote= |archive-date=2017-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512014520/http://rthk9.rthk.hk/broadcast75/topic05c.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。關西蒙未幾轉行從事會計、攝影、餐廳歌手等行業<ref name="娛樂圈容易搵錢 關西蒙怎能抗拒">{{cite news | title=娛樂圈容易搵錢 關西蒙怎能抗拒 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv595P2B4OmBy581NAsyb%2FgCV&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=11&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=26 | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1982-05-04 | accessdate=2021-06-22 | quote= | archive-date=2021-06-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628025723/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv595P2B4OmBy581NAsyb%2FgCV&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=11&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩年間曾被邀請拍攝廣告和電影，但都被他以不再是演藝人為由婉拒<ref name="娛樂圈容易搵錢 關西蒙怎能抗拒" />。他後來基於家庭因素而於1982年3月應時任商業電台第二台節目主任[[樂仕|樂仕]]重金邀約重返電台<ref name="娛樂圈容易搵錢 關西蒙怎能抗拒" /><ref>{{cite news | title=樂仕商二台組新班 鍾保羅關西蒙回巢 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv595P2B4OmBy5w0LwL8NQGAf&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=12&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=4 | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1982-02-28 | accessdate=2021-06-22 | quote= | archive-date=2021-06-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628021204/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=(%20verbatim_dc.collection:(%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22)%20)%20AND+(%20(%20allTermsMandatory:(true)%20OR+all_dc.title:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99)%20OR+all_dc.creator:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99)%20OR+all_dc.contributor:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%9