==個人生活==
關西蒙於1983年與任職航空公司的伍姓圈外人在油麻地婚姻註冊處結婚和行禮<ref>{{cite news | title=關西蒙快刀斬亂麻 趕在九月下旬結婚 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58StS6UNkXpigQZQzVYSxye&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=9 | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1983-08-09 | accessdate=2021-06-22 | quote= | archive-date=2021-06-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210630072729/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=(%20verbatim_dc.collection:(%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22)%20)%20AND+(%20(%20allTermsMandatory:(true)%20OR+all_dc.title:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99)%20OR+all_dc.creator:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99)%20OR+all_dc.contributor:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99)%20OR+all_dc.subject:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99)%20OR+fulltext:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99)%20OR+all_dc.description:(%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%92%99)%20)%20)&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58StS6UNkXpigQZQzVYSxye&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

